9 An Act relating to income tax; amending 68 O.S. 2021,
Section 2368.28, which relates to income tax refund
10 donation to the Indigent Veteran Burial Program;
reauthorizing donation for certain tax years;
11 amending 72 O.S. 2021, Section 63.19, which relates
to the Oklahoma Department of Veterans Affairs
12 Equipment and Capital Improvement Program;
reauthorizing donation for certain tax years;
13 updating statutory reference; updating statutory
language; providing an effective date; and declaring
14 an emergency.
